{"tid":1270032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人諗過五毛可能已經轉帶自殺風氣？","createTime":"2019-06-30T17:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T17:58:29.000Z","uid":204282,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c46fd8e7e084bb5b479674a7f1f3a896bdd9f0","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"呢幾日突然多左好多po講輕生<br />\n其實都理解到對住個仆街政府會無力<br />\n甚至絕望<br />\n唔否定可能有人的確想上黎開po做掙扎 求屌醒<br />\n但我地都要提防五毛<br />\n提防佢地帶風向<br />\n企喺佢地立場自殺係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">一個都嫌少</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n如果你感受到最近心理健康出現異常<br />\n不妨休息一下再戰<br />\n睇下膠野 搵時間比自己笑下<br />\n記住我地<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不流血 不受傷 不被捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n更重要係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地一個都不能少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"09e2541916886123e4ecf349943e9a1deaa3ecff","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d8ef0ba150de2a2b394b4e90555c194436fdbf2","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:47:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2fe30c4563c271ca1f4af3e7465197e012db28f3","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:48:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a6f469d494a4940a830567ee249d16519f4898d6","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:51:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"280b63de0e900f3c2858758ffe4b996bfd22dfbb","tid":1270032,"uid":204282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T17:52:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>推</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3cd36606288fe1caf35b0220d8f